name: TABLETOP GALLERY
description: Get ready to roll the dice in TABLETOP GALLERY. In this exciting title, you can choose from 3 games. POKER DICE SOLITAIRE FUTURE combines the single player experience of solitaire with the hand building mechanic of poker. SHUT THE BOX test your skills at eliminating the tiles on the game board to "shut the box". TOSS N GO pits you up against the computer or a second player to see who can be the first one to bank 100 or more points. Download this collection today, there is something for everyone!
